column6: Generic connector, double row, 02x06, odd/even pin numbering scheme (row 1 odd numbers, row 2 even numbers), script generated (kicad-library-utils/schlib/autogen/connector/)

TT130RGC17B is a color round active matrix and touch screen with capacitance thin film transistor(TFT)liquid crystal display(LCD)that uses amorphous silicon TFT as a switching device. This TFT LCD has a 1.3inch diagonally measured active display area with (240 horizontal by 240 vertical pixels)resolution.
